      "CreatedBy" : "<CREATED_BY_EMAIL>",
      "Description" : "Invokes AWS Lambda <LAMBDA_FUNCTION_NAME> (us-east-1) which fetches the most recent S&P 500 Strategic Rebalance PDF from S3 and emails it to the distribution list via Amazon SES. Runs after WATCH_REBALANCE_REPORT_S3 confirms a new report has landed. Recipients and sender are configured on the Lambda; this job's payload only specifies bucket and prefix.\\n\\n",
      "RunAs" : "JOG-AWS-LAMBDA-EAST1",
